5. As a user special characters and numbers should not be allowed in the first name, middle name, last name, birth month, birth day, and birth year fields

6. As a user I should be limited to 20 characters for first, last and middle names

7. As a user I should be limited to 10 characters for birth month

8. As a user I should be required to enter no less and no more than two characters for Day of Birth

9. As a user I should be required to enter no less and no more than four characters for year of birth

